Cost estimate of the workshop in four steps
With the Auda tool, Audatex ensures that the user receives a cost estimate in just four steps: identification of the vehicle, search of the spare part, creation and creation of a cost estimate.
Easy handling of these systems is a fundamental condition, especially to convince older professionals who are more or less opposed to the use of these new computer techniques.
The database includes 1,034 vehicles, 666 of which are passenger vehicles, 109 off-road vehicles, 137 motorcycles, 78 small vans and 44 trucks.
